.NET Framework 3.5.name: VRTK_BaseObjectControlAction
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: The Base Object Control Action script is an abstract class that all object control action scripts inherit.
.NET Framework 3.5.remarks: As this is an abstract class, it cannot be applied directly to a game object and performs no logic.
